<%= render "page_hero",
  title: "Our Story",
  subtitle: "Rooted in the Prairies. Built on trust. Dedicated to your everyday wellness."
%>

<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="row g-5 align-items-center">
    <!-- Story Column -->
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-7">
      <div class="prose">
        <p class="lead">
          Prairie Naturals was born in Winnipeg with a simple yet powerful vision:
          to create products that blend nature’s best with uncompromising quality,
          designed to enrich your everyday life.
        </p>
        <p>
          From our very first collection, we committed to sourcing responsibly,
          partnering only with suppliers who share our values of sustainability,
          transparency, and integrity. Every product is carefully tested to ensure
          it meets our high standards for safety, effectiveness, and ethical sourcing.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our customers aren’t just buyers—they’re collaborators in our journey.
          Your feedback inspires innovation, influences our collections,
          and ensures that what we offer truly supports your well-being.
        </p>
        <p>
          Today, we’re proud to be more than just a local business.
          We’re a trusted wellness partner, dedicated to helping you feel your best
          every day—naturally, authentically, and sustainably.
        </p>
        <p class="fw-semibold text-primary mt-4">
          Thank you for making us part of your routine. Together, we’re building
          a healthier, more conscious community.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats Column -->
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-5">
      <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="stat-card shadow-sm text-center p-4 rounded-4 bg-light">
            <div class="stat display-5 fw-bold text-primary">98%</div>
            <div class="label small text-muted">On-time Deliveries</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="stat-card shadow-sm text-center p-4 rounded-4 bg-light">
            <div class="stat display-5 fw-bold text-primary">4.8<span class="fs-6">/5</span></div>
            <div class="label small text-muted">Customer Satisfaction</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="stat-card shadow-sm text-center p-4 rounded-4 bg-light">
            <div class="stat display-5 fw-bold text-primary">2019</div>
            <div class="label small text-muted">Year Founded</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6">
          <div class="stat-card shadow-sm text-center p-4 rounded-4 bg-light">
            <div class="stat display-5 fw-bold text-primary">500+</div>
            <div class="label small text-muted">Products Curated</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
